<h1>Welcome to BarK Along!</h1>

<img src="https://www.123freevectors.com/wp-content/uploads/new/animals/370-cartoon-dog-vector-image.png" alt='BarK_mascot' style='width:15%;height:15%'><br>

<h3>What can you use BarK Along! for?</h3>
<ul>
  <li>To give a shout out to an awesome bar you found with a spectacular view!</li>
  <li>Invite others to share the special on margaritas you found at a happy hour!</li>
  <li>Or to simply flag others about the fire hydrant in the corner that's available for a quick tinkle.</li>
</ul>

<% if current_user %>
<% @user = User.find(session[:user_id]) %>
  <h3>Welcome back, <%=@user.f_name%>! </h3>
  <form action='/sessions/logout' method='post'>
    <input type='hidden' name='_method' value='delete'>
    <input type='submit' value='Sign Out'>
  </form>
<% else %>
  <a href="/users/new">Register New User</a><br>
  <a href="/sessions/new">Returning User Sign-In</a><br>
<% end %>
